      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario matches COU in geometry, loading, and material; any differences bridged by documented extrapolation argument.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the COU: same non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw geometry, same ASTM F1717 protocol, same material lot. No extrapolation beyond the validated scenario is required for the regulatory submission."
